        <title>被生命所厌弃（中文填词）</title>
        <link>https://hongyun-yu.github.io/Hugo-dev/p/%E8%A2%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E6%89%80%E5%8E%8C%E5%BC%83%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87%E5%A1%AB%E8%AF%8D/</link>
